{"tid":293862,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[慎入] 南非有隻羊生咗隻人形羊","createTime":"2017-06-22T13:34:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-23T15:29:32.000Z","uid":37125,"like":19,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4fb7707f86bd122c3fee035ca51fb8579cef97e0","tid":293862,"uid":37125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T13:34:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Superstitious villagers living in fear after sheep gives birth to 'half-human half-beast' creature that was 'sent by the devil'<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2017/06/22/11/41A2273C00000578-4628494-image-m-56_1498128089633.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fpix%2F2017%2F06%2F22%2F11%2F41A2273C00000578-4628494-image-m-56_1498128089633.jpg&h=58c7f8bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2017/06/22/13/41A2569C00000578-4628494-image-a-1_1498134710712.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fpix%2F2017%2F06%2F22%2F13%2F41A2569C00000578-4628494-image-a-1_1498134710712.jpg&h=538426af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2017/06/22/13/41A2567200000578-4628494-image-a-2_1498134735183.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fpix%2F2017%2F06%2F22%2F13%2F41A2567200000578-4628494-image-a-2_1498134735183.jpg&h=49645015&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nChief Director of Veterinary Services Dr Lubabalo Mrwebi admitted that at first glance the lamb which was born dead did resemble a human being but was not part human.<br />\n<br />\nDr Mrwebi said: 'We can confirm this not a hoax photo but that the severely deformed lamb was born by a sheep in Lady Frere this week which at a glance resembles a human form.<br />\n<br />\n'It is not however human but a deformed stillborn lamb sired by a sheep and was subsequently infected by a Rift Valley Fever at an early stage of its pregnancy.<br />\n<br />\n'It is worth noting that a sheep has 28 pairs of chromosomes while humans have 23 pairs which is important in dispelling the myth that a union of a sheep ovum and a human sperm can lead to a development of a viable life form.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-4628494/South-African-sheep-births-half-human-half-beast.html?ito=social-facebook\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailymail.co.uk%2Fnews%2Farticle-4628494%2FSouth-African-sheep-births-half-human-half-beast.html%3Fito%3Dsocial-facebook&d=2SecmFy%2BHa07roBAaDUWiDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=1b56b089\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-4628494/South-African-sheep-births-half-human-half-beast.html?ito=social-facebook</a>"},{"pid":"e15f15e216f49027013561ffc9a7b76f1c0e393f","tid":293862,"uid":1582,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T13:36:41.000Z","msg":"邊個屌羊"},{"pid":"1134c7adbed3866203cf8e99e6d1cc2cadf4f492","tid":293862,"uid":59163,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T13:37:47.000Z","msg":"似豬多d"},{"pid":"914814cda9f5aedccfebe5f275ec09d1c9c2b2f3","tid":293862,"uid":58099,"like":120,"dislike":3,"score":117,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T13:38:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>邊個屌羊</blockquote><br />\n羊咩1234"},{"pid":"d95c7e7840ca60f3c85eb96ed520f75630e496c1","tid":293862,"uid":103405,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T13:38:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf8aae5b7c3b2e94100fb5715a9122efbc84f3bc","tid":293862,"uid":29689,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T13:38:32.000Z","msg":"諗起套戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed049c8c61dca1